{"type": "article", "id": 28701, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。PS：我们认为这个世界的重要性不应该有绝对的等级，重点是看得更多，探索更多。", "date": "2016-06-25T11:06:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 28729, "name": "脱欧"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154203ic2saX4PWHEZyt6G.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、英国决定退出欧盟</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021541463bB5fEe4gmW9IyoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Rob Stothard/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">英国伦敦，“留欧”支持者紧张地等待结果公布。最终公投以 52% 对 48% 的结局决定了英国脱离欧盟的命运，随后首相卡梅伦宣布将于十月辞职。<b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、盐城风雹灾害</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154147UFpDei62c4ZMPmrk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">常州晚报 吴恺/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">江苏省盐城市，记者实拍灾区。常州消防官兵在小学操场上席地而睡，灾民被安置在不远处的教室里。 <b><br></b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、委内瑞拉或将启动总统罢免公投</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154148wF9KnyMWxmJTzufS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">JUAN BARRETO/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">委内瑞拉加拉加斯，反对派民众在全国选举委员会大厦前高喊反政府口号，等待罢免总统马杜罗公投的申请结果。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、长征七号发射倒计时</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154149u2cyoC9nz6O5pi4a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">中新社 秦宪安/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">海南文昌航天发射场，承载着长征七号运载火箭与搭载载荷组合体的活动发射平台安全转运至发射塔架。长征七号计划 6 月 25 日至 29 日择机发射，执行首次飞行试验任务。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、西班牙大选在即</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154149CxDbrs5RGU1z3dML.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Susana Vera/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">西班牙马德里，现任首相拉霍伊（Mariano Rajoy）在所属的人民党（People's Party）竞选集会上发言。西班牙将于当地时间 26 日重新举行议会选举，各党派纷纷举行大选前最后的竞选集会。</p>\n<h2>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、2017 春夏巴黎男装周</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154152cyuF5MNXBR9dhgaG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">FRANCOIS GUILLOT/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Comme des Garçons 品牌秀场。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154153QnFmGkVg8q1jy5Az.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">PATRICK KOVARIK/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Givenchy 品牌秀场。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154154vJQlzaf2dZKFINb8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Antonio de Moraes Barros Filho/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Louis Vuitton 品牌秀场。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154155HDz6VUx3SORPLcGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">YuYang/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154157KxlwqMeJOEgCGNdj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Christian Vierig/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154157aS3EYhLj17tvoKUy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Jacopo Raule/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">时尚街拍。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、音乐节帐篷</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154200TL2QH18SqcMriz9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">英国萨默塞特（Somerset），格拉斯顿伯里音乐节（Glastonbury ）举办地搭起五颜六色的帐篷。据报道，近些天来雨水和泥土让音乐节举办场地泥泞不堪，但仍阻挡不了乐迷们的热情，不断有人抵达扎营。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、北京东华门夜市正式闭市</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154201oF2PsAKEY8a0NtuZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">北京青年报 魏彤/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">北京东华门夜市，“老滕家”过桥米线摊位前的食客排起了长长的队伍，人们纷纷在最后一天专门来此品尝即将消失的口味并与过桥米线的掌门人滕老师傅拍照合影。闭市后东城区相关部门将在原址启动道路设施改造工程，恢复道路功能。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、菲律宾庆祝圣约翰日</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021542022gu0myYl7rceBRw3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Romeo Ranoco/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">菲律宾马尼拉，当地民众庆祝圣约翰日，在街头泼水祈福。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、冰川上的人</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154202uWDX587ICKfeGR9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Jassen Todorov/Solent News Photo Agency/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Vatna 冰川是冰岛最大的冰川，两名勇敢的徒步旅行者在充斥着致命裂缝的巨大冰川表面行走，和壮丽的冰川相比显得非常渺小。<br></p>\n\n"}